illinger]] |[[Princeton University]] |1984 |---- |[[Horst Ludwig Störmer]] |[[Columbia University]] |1999 |---- |[[Harry Swinney]] |[[University of Texas at Austin]] |1992 |---- |[[Jan Tauc]] |[[Brown University]] |1992 |---- |[[Gareth Thomas (materials scientist)|Gareth Thomas]] |[[MMFX Technologies Corporation]] |1983 |---- |[[David Thouless]] |[[University of Washington]] |1995 |---- |[[Daniel C. Tsui]] |[[Princeton University]] |1987 |---- |[[David Turnbull (materials scientist)|David Turnbull]] |[[Harvard University]] |1968 |---- |[[Dale Van Harlingen]] |[[University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign]] |2003 |---- |[[Klaus von Klitzing]] |[[Max Planck Institute for Solid State Research]] |1990 |---- |[[George Watkins (scientist)|George Watkins]] |[[Lehigh University]] |1988 |---- |Richard Webb |[[University of South Carolina]] |1996 |---- |[[Alvin Weinberg]] |[[Oak Ridge Associated Universities]] |1961 |---- |[[Maw-Kuen Wu]] |[[Academia Sinica (Taiwan)]] |2004 |---- |}
